  <entry>
    <title>HTML面试题</title>
    <url>/2022/03/18/HTML%E9%9D%A2%E8%AF%95%E9%A2%98/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h5 id="html标签的类型（head，-body，-Doctype）-他们的作用是什么"><a href="#html标签的类型（head，-body，-Doctype）-他们的作用是什么" class="headerlink" title="html标签的类型（head， body，!Doctype） 他们的作用是什么"></a>html标签的类型（head， body，!Doctype） 他们的作用是什么</h5><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">!Doctype 告诉浏览器关于页面是使用哪个版本的html进行编写的</span><br><span class="line">head 头部元素的容器，大多数头部标签内容不会显示在页面上，一般含有&lt;title&gt;、&lt;meta&gt;、&lt;link&gt;等标签</span><br><span class="line">body 定义文档的主体，包含文档所有的内容，支持html全局属性和事件属性</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<span id="more"></span>

<h5 id="行内元素有哪些？块级元素有哪些？-空-void-元素有哪些？"><a href="#行内元素有哪些？块级元素有哪些？-空-void-元素有哪些？" class="headerlink" title="行内元素有哪些？块级元素有哪些？ 空(void)元素有哪些？"></a>行内元素有哪些？块级元素有哪些？ 空(void)元素有哪些？</h5><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">行内元素：span、img、input...</span><br><span class="line">块级元素：div、footer、header、section、p、h1...h6...</span><br><span class="line">空元素：br、hr...</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h5 id="H5新特性"><a href="#H5新特性" class="headerlink" title="H5新特性"></a>H5新特性</h5><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">1.媒体播放的 video 和 audio</span><br><span class="line">2.绘画 canvas</span><br><span class="line">3.增强表单控件 date、time、email、search、color</span><br><span class="line">4.语意化标签 article、footer、header、nav、section</span><br><span class="line">5.本地存储 localStorage 和 sessionStorage</span><br><span class="line">6.全双工通信协议 websocket</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Ajax 轮询：</span><br><span class="line">轮询是在特定的的时间间隔（如每1秒），由浏览器对服务器发出HTTP请求，然后由服务器返回最新的数据给客户端的浏览器。</span><br><span class="line">缺点：浏览器需要不断的向服务器发出请求，然而HTTP请求可能包含较长的头部，其中真正有效的数据可能只是很小的一部分，显然这样会浪费很多的带宽等资源。</span><br><span class="line">websocket：</span><br><span class="line">浏览器和服务器只需要完成一次握手，两者之间就直接可以创建持久性的连接，并进行双向数据传输。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h5 id="html5语义化好处"><a href="#html5语义化好处" class="headerlink" title="html5语义化好处"></a>html5语义化好处</h5><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;title&gt;、&lt;header&gt;、&lt;footer&gt;、&lt;article&gt;、&lt;main&gt;、&lt;section&gt;、&lt;nav&gt;</span><br><span class="line">1.易于用户阅读，样式丢失的时候能让页面呈现清晰的结构。</span><br><span class="line">2.有利于SEO，根据标签来确定内容的权重。</span><br><span class="line">3.方便屏幕阅读器解析，如盲人阅读器根据语义渲染网页</span><br><span class="line">5.有利于开发和维护，语义化更具可读性，代码更好维护，与CSS3关系更和谐。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h5 id="audio-标签"><a href="#audio-标签" class="headerlink" title="audio 标签"></a>audio 标签</h5><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">常用属性：</span><br><span class="line">src 播放的音乐的url地址</span><br><span class="line">preload 预加载</span><br><span class="line">loop 循环播放</span><br><span class="line">controls 是否显示控制按钮</span><br><span class="line">autoplay 自动播放</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
]]></content>
      <categories>
        <category>前端 —— 基础</category>
      </categories>
      <tags>
        <tag>面试</tag>
        <tag>HTML</tag>
      </tags>
  </entry>
  <entry>
    <title>JS作用域+this指向+原型考题</title>
    <url>/2022/03/19/JS%E4%BD%9C%E7%94%A8%E5%9F%9F+this%E6%8C%87%E5%90%91+%E5%8E%9F%E5%9E%8B%E8%80%83%E9%A2%98/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h5 id="前提"><a href="#前提" class="headerlink" title="前提"></a>前提</h5><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">function fun()&#123;</span><br><span class="line">	this.x = 123;</span><br><span class="line">    console.log(111111);</span><br><span class="line">    return &#x27;aaaaaa&#x27;;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">console.log(fun);  //输出：函数体，不会执行函数</span><br><span class="line">console.log(fun());  //输出：111111 aaaaaa 执行函数，this指向window</span><br><span class="line">console.log(new fun());  //输出：111111 fun&#123;&#125; </span><br><span class="line">//new fun() 是一个对象，this指向这个对象</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<span id="more"></span>

<p>考题一：</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">function Foo()&#123;</span><br><span class="line">	getName = function()&#123;console.log(1)&#125; //注意是全局的window.  不是new Foo()的</span><br><span class="line">	return this;  //返回的是window</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">Foo.getName = function()&#123;console.log(2)&#125;  //Foo没加括号，函数并没有执行</span><br><span class="line">Foo.prototype.getName = function()&#123;console.log(3)&#125;</span><br><span class="line">var getName = function()&#123;console.log(4)&#125;</span><br><span class="line">  //声明变量 &gt; 声明普通函数 这句执行，下一句不会执行</span><br><span class="line">function getName()&#123;</span><br><span class="line">	console.log(5)</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">Foo.getName();    //2</span><br><span class="line">getName(); 		  //4</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">//这句话之前执行了getName = function()&#123;console.log(1)&#125;，</span><br><span class="line">将会覆盖var getName = function()&#123;console.log(4)&#125;</span><br><span class="line">//Foo()返回window</span><br><span class="line">Foo().getName();  //1     </span><br><span class="line">getName();		  //1</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">new Foo().getName();//3</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>考题二：（头条考题）</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">var o = &#123;</span><br><span class="line">	a:10,</span><br><span class="line">	b:&#123;</span><br><span class="line">		a:2,</span><br><span class="line">		fn:function()&#123;</span><br><span class="line">			console.log( this.a ); // 2</span><br><span class="line">			console.log( this );   //代表b对象</span><br><span class="line">		&#125;</span><br><span class="line">	&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">o.b.fn();</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>考题三：</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">window.name = &#x27;ByteDance&#x27;;</span><br><span class="line">function A()&#123;</span><br><span class="line">	this.name = 123;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">A.prototype.getA = function()&#123;</span><br><span class="line">	console.log( this );</span><br><span class="line">	return this.name + 1;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">//注意函数加不加括号的区别</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">let a = new A();</span><br><span class="line">let funcA = a.getA; </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">//a.getA后面不加括号，返回的是函数体</span><br><span class="line">相对于let funcA = function()&#123;</span><br><span class="line">	console.log( this );  //this指的是window</span><br><span class="line">	return this.name + 1;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">funcA();  //输出：window</span><br><span class="line">console.log(funcA());  //输出：ByteDance1</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">let a = new A();</span><br><span class="line">let funcA = a.getA(); //执行函数，this指的是A</span><br><span class="line">console.log(funcA);    //输出：124</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>考题四：</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">var length = 10;</span><br><span class="line">function fn()&#123;</span><br><span class="line">	return this.length + 1;   //this指向window</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">var obj = &#123;</span><br><span class="line">	length:5,</span><br><span class="line">	test1:function()&#123;</span><br><span class="line">		return fn();</span><br><span class="line">	&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">obj.test2 = fn;</span><br><span class="line">//相对于在obj里面加了一个</span><br><span class="line">test2:function()&#123;</span><br><span class="line">		return this.length + 1;  </span><br><span class="line">	&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">console.log( obj.test1() );  	//11</span><br><span class="line">console.log( fn()===obj.test2() ); 	 //11 ！= 6 输出：false</span><br><span class="line">console.log( obj.test1() == obj.test2() ); //false</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      <categories>
        <category>JS重难点突破</category>
      </categories>
      <tags>
        <tag>JS</tag>
      </tags>
  </entry>
  <entry>
    <title>JS作用域</title>
    <url>/2022/03/19/JS%E4%BD%9C%E7%94%A8%E5%9F%9F/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h5 id="基本规则"><a href="#基本规则" class="headerlink" title="基本规则"></a>基本规则</h5><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">1. 除了函数外，js是没有块级作用域。</span><br><span class="line">2. 作用域链：内部可以访问外部的变量，但是外部不能访问内部的变量。</span><br><span class="line">	 注意：如果内部有，优先查找到内部，如果内部没有就查找外部的。</span><br><span class="line">3. 注意声明变量是用var还是没有写（window.）</span><br><span class="line">4. 注意：js有变量提升的机制【变量悬挂声明】</span><br><span class="line">5. 优先级：声明变量 &gt; 声明普通函数 &gt; 参数 &gt; 变量提升</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<span id="more"></span>

<h5 id="易错点"><a href="#易错点" class="headerlink" title="易错点"></a>易错点</h5><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">(function() &#123;          //匿名函数</span><br><span class="line">	var a = b = 10;    //b其实是全局变量</span><br><span class="line">&#125;)()</span><br><span class="line">console.log(a); //出错，无法找到</span><br><span class="line">console.log(b);  //10</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">function fun()&#123;   //var str; 变量提升，你看不见，js独有的机制</span><br><span class="line">    console.log(str);  //undefined</span><br><span class="line">    var str = &#x27;你好吗&#x27;;</span><br><span class="line">    console.log(str);  //你好吗</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">fun();</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h5 id="面试的时候怎么看"><a href="#面试的时候怎么看" class="headerlink" title="面试的时候怎么看"></a>面试的时候怎么看</h5><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">1. 本层作用域有没有此变量【注意变量提升】</span><br><span class="line">2. 注意：js除了函数外没有块级作用域</span><br><span class="line">3. 普通声明函数是不看写函数的时候顺序</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>考题一：</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">function c()&#123;</span><br><span class="line">	var b = 1;</span><br><span class="line">	function a()&#123;</span><br><span class="line">		console.log( b );  //本层作用域有没有此变量【注意变量提升】</span><br><span class="line">		var b = 2;</span><br><span class="line">		console.log( b );     </span><br><span class="line">	&#125;</span><br><span class="line">	a();</span><br><span class="line">	console.log( b );</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">c();</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">输出：underfined  2  1</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>考题二：</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">var name = &#x27;a&#x27;;  //起迷惑作用</span><br><span class="line">(function()&#123;  //var name;</span><br><span class="line">	if( typeof name == &#x27;undefined&#x27; )&#123;//内部有name,变量提升，if和for没有块级作用域</span><br><span class="line">		var name = &#x27;b&#x27;;</span><br><span class="line">		console.log(&#x27;111&#x27;+name);   //输出：111b</span><br><span class="line">	&#125;else&#123;</span><br><span class="line">		console.log(&#x27;222&#x27;+name);</span><br><span class="line">	&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;)()</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>例证：</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">console.log(a);  //undefined</span><br><span class="line">if (false) &#123;    //不执行，但a会变量提升，因为if没有块级作用域</span><br><span class="line">    var a = 0;   </span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">console.log(a);   //undefined</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>考题三：优先级：声明变量 &gt; 声明普通函数 &gt; 参数 &gt; 变量提升</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">function fun()&#123;</span><br><span class="line">	var a = 10;</span><br><span class="line">	function a()&#123;&#125;</span><br><span class="line">	console.log( a );  //输出：10</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">fun();</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">function fun()&#123;</span><br><span class="line">	var a = 10;</span><br><span class="line">	var a = function a()&#123;&#125;</span><br><span class="line">	console.log( a );  //输出：f ()&#123;&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">fun();</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">function fun() &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        console.log(a);  //输出：f a()&#123;&#125;</span><br><span class="line">        var a = 10;   //声明普通函数 &gt; 变量提升  普通声明函数是不看写函数的时候顺序</span><br><span class="line">        function a() &#123;&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">fun();</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">function fun(a) &#123;  //声明普通函数 &gt; 参数   </span><br><span class="line">        console.log(a); //输出：f a()&#123;&#125;</span><br><span class="line">        function a() &#123;&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">fun(100);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
]]></content>
